cisco </LOCATION>. Police said it could take two days to complete the cleanup. The line could be reopened later today, <ORGANIZATION> Southern </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Pacific </ORGANIZATION> spokesman <PERSON> Jim </PERSON> <PERSON> Loveland </PERSON> said.
